{"type":"message","id":"3689d2c2","parentId":"6eb54e32","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:36:34.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor shows:\n- Usage: 62% (threshold is 60%)\n- Total tokens: 200,000\n- Used tokens: 123,641\n- Action: \"monitoring\"\n\nThis means we're at 62% context usage, which is above the 60% threshold. The context manager is in \"monitoring\" mode but might need to take action. Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md file to see if there's anything specific that needs attention.","thinkingSignature":"f1a8dfb7d545dc1dce200e1ee1836c8f6ec073c45e0ba12e3636fff3109cb24f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qawyc7d39puk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":503,"output":139,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37644,"cost":{"input":0.00015089999999999998,"output":0.0001668,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00142776}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773905790125}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2e4c02d","parentId":"3689d2c2","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:36:34.986Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qawyc7d39puk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Context Manager Check\n\n- Run session_status to check current context usage\n- If context > 60%, consider saving memory and preparing for session switch\n- Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n- Update ~/proactivity/memory/working-buffer.md if needed\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read ./skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md\n- Use ~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside ~/self-improving/ changed since the last reviewed change, return HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n## Proactivity Check\n\n- Read ~/proactivity/heartbeat.md\n- Re-check active blockers, promised follow-ups, stale work, and missing decisions\n- Ask what useful check-in or next move would help right now\n- Message the user only when something changed or needs a decision\n- Update ~/proactivity/session-state.md after meaningful follow-through\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773905794983}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ac35fa4","parentId":"f2e4c02d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:36:40.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Context usage is at 62%, which is above the 60% threshold. According to the HEARTBEAT.md, I should:\n1. Check session_status for current context usage\n2. Consider saving memory and preparing for session switch\n3. Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n\nThe current usage is 62% which is above threshold. Let me check if there are any active tasks in the proactivity session-state that need attention.","thinkingSignature":"81e0a1ac6fc3d4a3c4d9d40c5533169d79da80bb1ab65212c4f1f255466ff51c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7fk5tlkhil4d_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\proactivity\\session-state.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":887,"output":136,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38025,"cost":{"input":0.00026609999999999996,"output":0.00016319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00153936}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773905794986}}
