{"type":"message","id":"4aa57d36","parentId":"9a373262","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:36:50.840Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_czwhf2wux5gh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-19 工作日志\n\n## 发现问题：Browser 自动化打开大量标签页\n\n- **现象**：Chrome 有几十个打开的标签页，包括 news.google.com、百度新闻等\n- **原因**：OpenClaw 的 browser 自动化工具被某个定时任务（如新闻推送）调用，但浏览器没有正确关闭\n- **解决**：手动关闭了所有标签页并停止 browser 自动化\n\n## 自启动问题\n\n- 启动脚本已修复：从 `start node` 改为直接调用 `node`\n- 使用 Windows Startup folder 而非计划任务\n- 脚本路径：`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Start Menu\\Programs\\Startup\\OpenClaw\\gateway.cmd`\n\n## 定时任务状态\n\n- 大部分失败（权限/配置问题）\n- Context Monitor 每5分钟运行 ✅\n- Daily Gateway Restart 每天5点 ✅\n\n## 资源状态\n\n- 157 个活动会话（大部分是旧的）\n- 多个 PowerShell 进程运行中\n\n## 上下文切换 (13:32)\n\n- 主会话 context 使用率达到 65%，触发自动切换\n- 启动新 subagent 会话继续工作\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773905810836}}
{"type":"message","id":"d87d9e01","parentId":"4aa57d36","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:36:57.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the memory, there's been a context switch earlier today at 13:32 when context reached 65%. The current usage is 62%, which is still above the 60% threshold but below the previous high of 65%.\n\nThe context monitor job is running and showing:\n- Current usage: 62%\n- Threshold: 60%\n- Action: monitoring\n\nThis is slightly above threshold but not critical yet. The previous context switch happened at 65%, so we have some headroom. Since this is just a monitoring check and usage isn't dramatically higher than before, I should acknowledge the monitoring state but not trigger any immediate action unless it gets higher.\n\nLet me also check if there's anything urgent in the proactivity folder.","thinkingSignature":"4a30ca1e64dedc56da12a7ed4d080e98c99af93723d846e917dd691a48f4317f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_swcm6flp9cu6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"type C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\proactivity\\heartbeat.md 2>nul || echo \"File not found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1370,"output":200,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38572,"cost":{"input":0.00041099999999999996,"output":0.00023999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017610599999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773905810840}}
